'''Mark Arthur Cheetham''' (born 1954) is professor in the department of art at [[University College, University of Toronto|University College]], University of Toronto. Cheetham is a specialist in [[artwriting]] and modern and [[contemporary art]].<ref>http://www.uc.utoronto.ca/contacts/mark_cheetham</ref><ref>http://art.utoronto.ca/faculty/faculty/mark-a-cheetham/</ref>
